name: Visual Studio Serialized Performance Report
summary: Learn about .VSPS files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: VSPS files are generated by the Visual Studio Profiler. To save a VSPS file in the Profiler, right-click a VSP report and choose "Save Analyzed..." from the drop down menu.
NOTE: VSP files may be very large in size. Therefore, developers sometimes keep VSPS files locally while deleting or archiving VSP files.

description: Developer file created by Visual Studio, a software development IDE; saves summary data collected from analyzing a performance report (.VSP file); enables the data to be saved without having to re-generate it again from the VSP file.
